{"title":"赞美中国的歌——为庆祝中华人民共和国成立十二周年作","authors":["阿列克斯·恰奇"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美中国的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为庆祝中华人民共和国成立十二周年作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔阿尔巴尼亚〕阿列克斯·恰奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“把困难留给自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把方便让给别人，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自私自利之徒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听到胆战心惊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们所要的新世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在中国诞生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像浩瀚的长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛无尽，澎湃奔腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们用千万只水桶灌溉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使旱地有了水分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用数不尽的筐筐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为田垅施肥下粪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渠道密如蛛网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水井钻进地层。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到四川盆地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边际的绿浪滚滚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄龙已被锁住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浊浪正在变清；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云南的原始森林里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已滚动大小车轮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞍山的瑞烟袅袅上升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笼罩东北的广大村镇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切都是在中国看到的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心在沸腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管天空能晦暗多次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的太阳会拨开云层。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同我，同你，同中国人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界将会生存。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“把困难留给自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把方便让给别人，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要建设新世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要这样的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国啊，中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就在这条路上飞奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（范承祚译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}